data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom corner home. This home offers a beautifully updated kitchen with a huge island, and hardwood flooring throughout the first floor.  There is a gorgeous wall of windows in the living room with a sit-in bay. The back patio is a perfect place for entertaining with a built-in gas grill and fire pit. This home sits on 1/3 acre and has a side garage to make it feel even bigger. So close to great shopping, parks, and I88.
